WORMCOUNT Changelog
===================

version 0.8.1
------------------
* fixed issue when loading certain filetypes (mostly grayscale)
* alternate thresholding method in cases where median pixel is 0 after tophat transform
* support for grid images is still in beta

version 0.8.beta
----------------
* intial attempt at analyzing square grid images
* issues with worms that cross the grid boundaries (they are missed)
* added appropriate licences and made repository public

version 0.7.5
-------------
* fixed handling of truecolor images
* updated to work with newer Matlab versions (fileparts command changed)

version 0.7.4
-------------
* added support to set separate origin diameter

